// Package jni provides idiomatic Go bindings for the Java Native Interface (JNI).
//
// The root package exposes the idiomatic API: Env, VM, Class, Object, String,
// Array, MethodID, FieldID, Value, and related types. All JNI exceptions are
// converted to Go errors. Thread safety is handled via VM.Do().
//
// The raw CGo bindings live in the capi/ sub-package. Most users should not
// need to import capi/ directly.
//
// Code in this package is generated by jnigen from spec/jni.yaml and
// spec/overlays/jni.yaml. Do not edit generated files; edit the spec and
// overlay instead, then run `make jni`.
package jni
